The paper discusses automatic rumor detection using machine learning techniques, which falls under the natural language processing (NLP) domain. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves data mining and information retrieval techniques, which are covered in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) respectively. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves analyzing social media data, which is covered in cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
